properties.Name: CustomerAccountProductDistributionChannel
properties.Description: The associated Channel(s) that provides product distribution services to the related customer account for the indicated period.

Columns.Name: CustomerAccountId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Customer Account.

Columns.Name: ProductId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Product.

Columns.Name: ChannelId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Channel.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date for which the associated product customer account distribution channel relationship exists.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date for which the associated product customer account distribution channel relationship exists.

Columns.Name: CustomerAccountProductDistributionChannelNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the distribution Channel servicing of the Customer Account for the Product indicated.
